 SOURCE CODE
 -----------
 Source code can be checked out from ccnx-trace repository.

 $ git clone https://code.google.com/p/ccnx-trace/

 This would create a directory named ccnx-trace


 INSTALLATION OVERVIEW
 ---------------------------
 It is recommended to install both server and client. However, they can be installed individually.

    $ cd ccnx-trace
    $ make all
    $ sudo make install



 UNINSTALLATION
 --------------
 The program can be uninstalled using make uninstall.

    $ cd ccnx-trace
    $ sudo make uninstall

            
 NOTES
 -----

 o Make sure you have ccnx and openssl-devel installed. Otherwise the installation will fail.

 o Please report installation issues at http://code.google.com/p/ccnx-trace/issues/
